snippet.title: Miramax
snippet.description: Welcome to the official YouTube channel for MIRAMAX, the studio that brought you Pulp Fiction, Clerks, City Of God, Good Will Hunting, Sin City, Amelie, Trainspotting, Kill Bill, No Country For Old Men and many more of your favorite films.  Subscribe today and come back everyday to watch clips and trailers and discover the latest for our upcoming films and TV series.
